{% extends "layouts/base.twig" %}
{% set title_name = "绑定密保卡 - 凤凰山庄" %}
{% block header %}
{% set menu_name = "userverify" %}
{% include "layouts/header.twig" %}
{% endblock %}
{% block left %}
{% include "layouts/left.twig" %}
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
    <div class="mod_right ">
  		<div class="send mfoot10">当前位置：<a href="/" class="ablack">首页</a> > 绑定密保卡</div>
        {% block usernav %}
        {% set nav_name = "matrixcard" %}
        {% include "layouts/user.twig" %}
        {% endblock %}
        <div class="usermod">
            <div class="mibaoka">
                <h3>绑定密保卡</h3>
                <p class="tip">
                    申请必读：<br>
                    1.密保卡将会与您的账号绑定，绑定之后，每次登陆都需要提供密保卡上的验证信息，没有密保卡您将无法登陆。<br>
                    2.每张密保卡只允许领取一次，如果您遗忘了密保卡，只能重新申请绑定，无法找回。<br>
                    3.如果您重新申请密保卡，您当前的密保卡将自动作废。
                </p>
                <div class="succ">
                    <p class="p1">密保卡绑定成功，正在自动下载您的密保卡，请稍候……</p>
                    <p class="p2"><a href="{{ this.createUrl('/matrixcard/creatematrixcard',{'gtime':gtime,'key':key})}}"><img src="{{ App.assets.Url }}/images/user/download.png" /></a></p>
                </div>
                <p class="foot">如果您忘记注册资料，请<a href="{{ this.createUrl('/appeal/create')}}" class="ablue">点击这里</a>填写申诉表。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        jQuery(function(){
            setTimeout("window.location=\"/matrixcard/creatematrixcard/gtime/{{ gtime }}/key/{{ key }}\"", 3000);
        });
    </script>
{% endblock %}
